Package ema_08_.crisisMod.clans

Class ClanManager

java.lang.Object
ema_08_.crisisMod.clans.ClanManager
public class ClanManager extends Object
Singleton manager class for handling clan operations and queries. Provides thread-safe methods for managing clans, checking memberships, and performing clan-related operations.
Version:
1.0
Author:
SchlangeGoto
